","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19589,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/26\/seven-five-takbir-salat-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":31949,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Seven and five Takbir in Eid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"'Amr ibn 'Awf reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pronounce takbir during the Eid prayer seven times before the recitation in the first cycle, and five times before the recitation in the second cycle. Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cThis tradition is acted upon by some of the people\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":30060,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/19\/malik-adab-duty-of-students\/","url_meta":{"origin":31949,"position":3},"title":"Malik on Adab: Duty of students to have good manners","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn 'Abdul Barr reported: Imam Malik ibn Anas, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cSurely, it is the duty of a student of knowledge to behave with dignity, calm, and reverence, and to follow the narrations of those who came before him.\u201d Source: Ja\u0304mi\u2019 Baya\u0304n al-\u2018Ilm 1\/543 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonlin